autotransform.thirdparty package

Submodules

autotransform.thirdparty.components module

An example module containing custom imports. Used via the custom_components config setting. All custom component imports should follow this structure. Component types that do not have any custom implementations do not need to be included (i.e. if there are no custom batchers, the BATCHERS variable can be left out.

Module contents

An example package showing how to set up modules for custom imports.
